## **_TIFFANY STRATTON DEF. CANDICE LERAE_**

Nia attacks Tiffy immediately, Trish Stratus runs out to save Tiffy but she also gets KOd and then stacked on top of Tiffy.

Nia squashes them both(as gently as she can). Then Charlotte leaves the commentary booth and stands over Tiffany.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/818f723f-f20f-4f4b-9a9c-27d398025c49/Screenshot_20250221_182407.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a66f576f-daf0-4396-a079-d6c69b373aac/Screenshot_20250221_184331.jpg)

Liv Morgan vs Naomi does not happen as Bianca Belair and Raquel Rodriguez get into the ring and a big brawl breaks out.

Then the Rock's truck pulls up.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/7832db53-193b-4acf-8e09-f2a63e608d5b/Screenshot_20250221_184315.jpg)

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/93e2f94c-8cc2-4589-a819-8d340ebf20ea/20250221_190205.jpg)

The Rock says Cody and him have become close friends over the past few months. He loves Cody and he thinks he's a great WWE Champion.

Now the Rock says that Ari Emmanuel basically says the Rock owns WWE.

So Cody being a great Champion isn't enough, the Rock wants Cody to be HIS corporate Champion.

The Rock can take Cody to the next level. The Rock wants Cody to be his BROTHER. When Cody told the Rock to "fk off" when he tried to replace him last year and slapped the Rock in the face, the Rock gained great respect for Cody.

He wants Cody Rhodes to go home and think about it. The Rock will be at Toronto, Canada waiting for Cody Rhodes response.

But Cody needs to remember that the one thing Dwayne wants more than anything in this world is Cody's soul.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/45dcad1e-cb3b-4f12-b8f3-b391cffeb4bb/20250221_191104.jpg)

