*   ## **_DIY vs PRETTY DEADLY GOES TO A NO CONTEST_**
    

Street Profits attack both teams leading to a no contest followed by MCMG coming out to try and make a save before getting whipped as well.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/af83fcc7-8d9f-45d2-b36e-9e92bcccaa6a/20250221_200243.jpg)

*   ## **_Damian Priest and Braun Strowman def. Solo Sikoa and Jacob Fatu_**
    

Jacob Fatu accidentally super kicks Solo Sikoa, gets thrown outside. Braun hits the Runaway Train Shoulder Tackle outside while Priest pins Solo to close Smackdown